==================================================
WHEN TO TEST
============

After every phase:

1. Build
2. Run
3. Test functionality
4. Fix issues
5. Commit to Git
6. Proceed to next phase

==================================================
PORTFOLIO VALUE
===============

By completing all phases, you demonstrate:

* React Frontend
